If your front door’s looking tired, grab a brush and I’ll show you how to make it look brand new. I’ll walk you through the exact steps I use to paint a front door so you get a smooth finish and no ugly brush marks. With the right tools and a couple pro tricks, you can boost your curb appeal in just one afternoon.

If you found this video helpful, please subscribe. Hope you enjoy. Cheers!
